Vending MAchine

Vending Machine should:

1. Accepts Coins

2. Gives item

3. Return Change


Class User():
	Behviour: 
			Bool RequestService():
				if User request service:
					return True
				else:
					return False
		
			SelectItem(Item)
				//Function to select items from Vending Machine
			
			PutCoin(Denomination)
				//Function to put coins into vending machine
				
			CollectItem():
				//Function to collect item
				
			CollectChange():
				//Function to collect change dispensed from  vending machine after purchase
				
Class Machine():
	Behviour: 
		
			AcceptsInput(Item)
				//Function to Accept item requested from user
			
			getsCoins(Denomination)
				//Function to get coins from User
				
			GiveBackCoin():
				//Function to return coin if amount is insufficient or not relavant
				
			ReturnChange():
				//Function to return change
				
			GiveItem():
				//Function to give item to user
				


